Invocation Name: doctor steve
des:
This simple skill tells you a random fun fact from Doctor Steve and the Weird Medicine Show. Get started by saying 'Alexa open doctor steve.' You can then say 'tell me a fun fact' to receive fun facts one by one, or you can say 'stop' to exit. You can also say 'help me' to get instructions at any time. Fact list updated regularly!

The information in this skill is provided for informational and educational purposes only. It is not a substitute for professional medical advice, treatment or diagnosis. Call your doctor to receive medical advice. If you think you may have a medical emergency, please dial your local emergency response phone number
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
